<plot>"Pogonya za Angelom" ("Runaway Angel") is the story of a well known Russian businessman's son, Ivan Arkhangelsky, who casually brings home a female assassin. The girl then kills his father and disappears, leaving all evidence of the crime pointing to Ivan. Ivan, running from the corrupt justice system, decides the only way to get his life back is to find the murderer himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?437018</url></doc>
